{"tid":1334441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【GUNDAM 00】 日本計劃建造太空電梯  預算10萬億日圓","createTime":"2019-07-20T06:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T07:29:14.000Z","uid":111253,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"34db838977b49965ed91337edad6db30206396af","tid":1334441,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:04:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190720/59780596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190720%2F59780596&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=a543397c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190720%2F59780596&h=d983dabf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190720/59780596</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>日本當前的太空計劃重點是探索小行星，探測器隼鳥2號本月上旬在距地球約2億4000公里的小行星龍宮着陸，採集經人工撞擊形成的隕石坑地表下樣本，並在本年底離開龍宮返回地球。日本另一個大計是打造不靠火箭進入宇宙的太空電梯，目標是在2050年建成，電梯從地面出發預料需時8天到達太空站，計劃料耗資10萬億日圓。</strong><br />\n<br />\n1萬港紙都唔洗就可以電梯上宇宙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   香港拎黎填海"},{"pid":"30419291f7c4d90bdee29696f6bb1e531ff7bac9","tid":1334441,"uid":111253,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:04:49.000Z","msg":"1萬<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">億</span></strong>港紙"},{"pid":"61ca4580c19b8153da5f7562d2da8ae4550ce047","tid":1334441,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20d8a68e3d7a2b5fd9af425e14ea8c9b430d9ed","tid":1334441,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019